  <thing id="rauETHostM" name="Host to Many" description="If Tesh is damaged by positive energy, he does not flee; instead, the energy drives away some of the many spirits inhabiting his body and protecting him. He loses his spectral aura ability for the duration of the turning. Additional positive energy damage in the round affects him normally. If the amount of positive energy damage would destroy him (reduce him to 0 hp), it instead permanently removes his spectral aura ability (though over time he can acquire more souls and rebuild it). These countless spirits flavor his other powers; for example, when he teleports, he transforms into a cloud of spirits, his necrotic blasts look like ribbons of shadow, and so on." compset="RaceSpec">
